fields.name: EndOfLifeDate
fields.description: The end of life date of the gallery image version Definition. This property can be used for decommissioning purposes. This property is updatable.

fields.name: ExcludeFromLatest
fields.description: If set to true, Virtual Machines deployed from the latest version of the Image Definition won't use this Image Version.

fields.name: PublishedDate
fields.description: The published date of the gallery image version Definition. This property can be used for decommissioning purposes. This property is updatable.
